item.description:
Hey guys, I've postponed 4/18's meetup to Satuday 4/24 because of the weather condition.

If you have never given me your cell phone number, pls email me your #. Tee times are 1:09, 1:18, 1:27 and 1:36. Let's meet in front of the club house at 12:55.

If you need to change your RSVP, please do so 24 hours prior to the event, when I can confirm with the golf club the exact number of people attending. Each person is responsible for one's green fee, and I will collect $1 from everyone for the meetup website fund.

The course rating is 72.7 and it has a slope rating of 132 on Bent grass. I have not played at this course. But from what I heard, it's not easy.
